# Group Articles
## Articles Collection [/api/v1/articles{?limit}{?olderthan}]

+ Parameters
    + limit (optional, number, `10`) ... maximum number of returned items
    + olderthan (optional, long, `1393496667000`) ... requesting older articles published before this date (Unix epoch time in milliseconds)

