# Group Statements
## Statements Collection [/api/v1/statements{?party}{?politician}{?limit}{?olderthan}]

+ Parameters
    + party (optional, id, `1`) ... filter only statements of specified party
    + politician (optional, id, `1`) ... filter only statements of specified politician
    + limit (optional, id, `10`) ... maximum number of returned items
    + olderthan (optional, string, `1393496667000`) ... requesting older statements published before this date

### List statements [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
           {
              "id":4554,
